xl2csv.py

Reads an Excel file and write a CSV file for each sheet.
(The main work is done by Python pandas module, so you will need that installed).
To see options, type:

 $ python xl2csv.py -h

Also included is csv2tsv.py,
which reads CSV files and converts them to TSV (TAB-separated values),
 optionally truncated to 7 chars to the columns line up.
To see options, type:

$ python csv2tsv.py -h

